headline.print_headline: Woman Is Dead After Dog Attack
headline.main: New Haven Woman Dies a Week After Being Mauled by 2 Dogs

snippet: The animals attacked a 53-year-old woman on their owner’s property in New Haven. The dogs will be euthanized, the police said.
abstract: Jocelyn G Winfrey, who was mutilated by dogs belonging to neighbor Hamilton Hicks in New Haven, dies week after attack.
